<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>专注计时器</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 主计时器页面 -->
    <div id="timer-page" class="page active">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="timer-card">
                <div class="activity-input">
                    <input type="text" id="activity-input" placeholder="输入你正在做的事情...">
                </div>
                <div class="timer-display">
                    <span id="minutes">00</span>
                    <span class="separator">:</span>
                    <span id="seconds">00</span>
                </div>
                <div class="timer-controls">
                    <button id="reset-btn" class="control-btn reset">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <path d="M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 0-6.74 2.74L3 8"></path>
                            <path d="M3 3v5h5"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <button id="play-pause-btn" class="control-btn play-pause start">
                        <svg class="play-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"></polygon>
                        </svg>
                        <svg class="pause-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="display: none;">
                            <rect x="6" y="4" width="4" height="16"></rect>
                            <rect x="14" y="4" width="4" height="16"></rect>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <button id="records-btn" class="control-btn records">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="status-indicator">
                    <span class="status-dot"></span>
                    <span id="status-text">STANDBY</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 记录页面 -->
    <div id="records-page" class="page">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="records-section">
                <div class="page-header">
                    <h2>活动记录</h2>
                    <button id="back-btn" class="back-btn">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"></polyline>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div id="records-list" class="records-list">
                    <!-- 记录将通过JavaScript动态添加 -->
                </div>
                <button id="clear-records" class="clear-btn">清空记录</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 浮窗元素 -->
    <div id="floating-window" class="floating-window">
        <div class="floating-timer">
            <span id="floating-minutes">00</span>:
            <span id="floating-seconds">00</span>
        </div>
        <div class="floating-activity" id="floating-activity">
            未设置活动
        </div>
        <div class="floating-controls">
            <button id="float-play-pause" class="float-btn play-pause">
                <svg class="play-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"></polygon>
                </svg>
                <svg class="pause-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="display: none;">
                    <rect x="6" y="4" width="4" height="16"></rect>
                    <rect x="14" y="4" width="4" height="16"></rect>
                </svg>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="floating-toggle">
            <button id="toggle-float" class="float-toggle-btn">关闭浮窗</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
# 专注计时器应用

一个具有科技感和液态玻璃效果的专注计时应用，支持计时、活动记录和浮窗显示功能。

## 功能特点

- ⏰ 精准计时器，支持分秒显示
- 📝 活动输入，实时放大显示
- 📋 活动记录保存
- 🪟 浮窗显示，可在其他应用上查看计时状态
- 🎨 液态玻璃质感界面，科技感强
- 📱 响应式设计，适配手机屏幕

## 本地运行

1. 进入项目目录
2. 启动本地服务器
   ```bash
   # 使用Python 3
   python -m http.server 8000
   
   # 或使用Python 2
   python -m SimpleHTTPServer 8000
   ```
3. 在浏览器中访问 http://localhost:8000

## 部署到免费托管平台

### 国外平台

#### 方法1: GitHub Pages

1. 在GitHub上创建一个新的仓库
2. 将项目文件上传到仓库
3. 在仓库设置中启用GitHub Pages，选择main分支
4. 等待部署完成，获得访问链接

#### 方法2: Vercel

1. 访问 https://vercel.com
2. 使用GitHub账号登录
3. 点击"New Project"
4. 选择"Import Git Repository"或直接拖放项目文件夹
5. 按照提示完成部署

#### 方法3: Netlify

1. 访问 https://netlify.com
2. 使用GitHub账号登录
3. 点击"Add new site"
4. 选择"Deploy manually"
5. 拖放项目文件夹到指定区域
6. 等待部署完成

